        <p>These appear to be <foreign>biruda</foreign>s of Narasiṃhavarman II Pallava, also attested in <ref target="INSPallava00054.xml">INSPallava00054</ref>, <ref target="INSPallava00060.xml"> INSPallava00060</ref>, and <ref target="INSPallava00063.xml">INSPallava00063</ref>.</p>
